{"tid":147491,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友想見家長","createTime":"2017-03-08T01:27:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-09T15:37:23.000Z","uid":58622,"like":1,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4cff85c5d0d03c2c8df73b8b74b720cb743c9dc3","tid":147491,"uid":58622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T01:27:00.000Z","msg":"我同佢一齊左3年,大家都係20歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />之前一直都無提呢件事,但近排開始俾説話我聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又話佢嘅朋友都有見過家長,又話畢業典禮都帶佢去...但我仲係覺得太快見唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,始終大家只有20歲,仲未去到結婚,無謂煩到屋企人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢又好似好想見咁,我就求其咁講就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />、究竟係我諗法有問題,定係佢諗得太快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利伸識左10年,已經視佢為終生伴侶"},{"pid":"3911078df5b7ade671b3d75c4b98aadffe9b941a","tid":147491,"uid":12514,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T01:28:21.000Z","msg":"唔見你應該仲有排煩"},{"pid":"091bdbd2565d25612c11046d5c1320e35193dda2","tid":147491,"uid":28002,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T01:30:43.000Z","msg":"未去到結婚又要視佢為終身伴侶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n視佢為終身伴侶咁怕乜嘢見家長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a7ca84faa134179adb9f0fb14c671d5c37a1aec","tid":147491,"uid":10453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T01:31:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未去到結婚又要視佢為終身伴侶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n視佢為終身伴侶咁怕乜嘢見家長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nTrue"},{"pid":"2868015fa2e941ceb1af110620718afa957da7e4","tid":147491,"uid":58622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T01:32:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔見你應該仲有排煩</blockquote><br />\n我都覺<img 